##  Examples in action

<code>

int a = 10;

int b = 20;

System.out.println(a > 20 && b > 10);
System.out.println(a > 20 || b > 10);
System.out.println(! (b > 10));
System.out.println(! (a > 20));

</code>

<p class="fragment roll-in">What does this print?</p>
<p class="fragment roll-in">
false<br/>
true<br/>
false<br/>
true<br/>
</p>
